<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039280" n="1"/>
  <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895">Ad <rs type="person">Joh. Jacobum Zörnlinum</rs>, <rs type="place">Sangallum</rs>.</note>
  <p> Amicissimi Domini <rs type="person">Ritsii</rs> istam ad te exaro epistolam, Zörnline optime, hac spe fretus, te illam utut ab ignoto venientem homine genigno tamen animo accepturum, et desiderium meum circa numerum demortuorum, de quo forte jam tecum co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicavit <rs type="person">Ritsius</rs> noster dilectus, haud <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gre expleturum esse. Humanissime igitur abs te peto, velis numerum mortuorum, initio seculi decimi septimi <abbr>h. e.</abbr> anno <date>1600</date><choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice> <date>1601<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice></date> vel <date>1610</date> <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr> natorum, in <rs type="biblio">catalogus</rs> rejicere; talem <rs type="biblio">catalogum</rs> pro <date>1630</date><choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> et <date>1640</date><choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>Dno</abbr> <rs type="person">Ritiio</rs> accepi, sed remoram injicit, quod quidam qui eis annis nati sunt adhuc vivunt, vellem enim cujusque <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tatem, quam vivendo attigit, scire ut dein possem long<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>vitatem vit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> human<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pro singulis annis per artem conjecturandi aliquo modo supputare. Laborem quem hac in re sustinebis decenti honorario remunerabor, gratumque animum per mutui officii redhostimenta, si qua se occasio pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>buerit, tibi testatum faciam. Hisce, quia tempus me deficit, valere te volo quam optime, et ut me inter Amicos tuos inposterum numerare velis obsecro.</p>
</div>
</body>
